_description:
 PURPOSE:
       Check that cheese runs and works correctly
 STEPS:
      1. Run cheese from the desktop icon. Does the icon look correct? 
      2. Make sure hamburger menu -> Help brings up the Cheese Help page
      3. See if cheese connects to any available webcams
      4. See if screenshots work. Check for the screenshots to be saved in $HOME/Pictures/Webcam/
      5. See if video recording works. Check for the video recordings to be saved in $HOME/Videos/Webcam/
 If there are any issues, please file them here: https://github.com/ubuntu/cheese/issues 


